<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04826</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROHIBITING DRAG RACING IN PUBLIC ROADS AND PRESCRIBING PENALTIES FOR VIOLATIONS THEREOF AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : " Drag Racing Ban Act "</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : States that drag racing, that involves the employment of two or more private motor vehicles driven side by side within a specified distance at accelerating speeds with the objective to outdo each other, or the employment of motor vehicles not necessarily driven side by side over a common course, is hereby declared banned or prohibited; Also includes those public utility vehicles randomly overtaking each other for the purpose of getting passengers first or merely for the purpose of outdistancing each other, is likewise prohibited.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CASTELO, WINSTON &quot;WINNIE&quot;</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-01-25</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Tambunting (084 2017-05-02)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2017-02-01</td></tr></table>